Description: Beyondcell computes a score summarizing the cell-based drug 
  sensitivity for each cell in your experiment and a subset of drugs of 
  interest. It also includes functions to prioritize drugs based on these scores 
  and visualize the results.
URL:
  https://gitlab.com/bu_cnio/beyondcell,
  https://beyondcell.bioinformatics.cnio.es
